1509395827-18x12.webp 18w" sizes="(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px" /></div><div class="kadence-blocks-gallery-item__caption">cosmetics filling machine</div></div></figure></div></li></ul></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Hot Filling Machine Construction Material</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Hot filling involves packing liquids at high temperatures (normally between 60°C and 140°C). So the materials that touch the liquid must be carefully chosen to ensure safety, durability, and hygiene. Npack strictly choose the material not only to meet the GMP, FDA, and also durability working in high temperature.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">316L Stainless Steel is one of the most common, reliable, and recommended choice for most food drink and cosmetics products.and the surface of treatment of the liquid contact parts are also important, such as electropolished&nbsp;finish;The seals and gaskets, we normally choose the PTFE / PFA&nbsp;,FKM / Viton and EPDM Rubber according to the liquid and product feature. A ceramic piston and valve is also one of the good choice for a cosmetics and pharmaceuticals liquid.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Hot Filling Machine industry application</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Hot filling machines are used in many industries to package products that needs sterlization and solid at room temperature.It is mostly application in the cosmetics , phamarceuticals and food industry.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In food industry, the hot filling is more applicaiton for the drinks and sauce, one is for sterilization and anther one is for long life keep.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In&nbsp;cosmetics, like for packing filling lipstick and lip gloss ,  when filling, mostly these products are in hot stage, for it is more easy to fill and after filling then cooling into its nature solid form.</p>



